{"id":"be618f46d8047a7659d552cc346df614ccfb936b326ddb6d28d78dbed88aa018","item_id":"3c43257e4f:0","text":"Creating Lights（创建灯光）"}
{"id":"a3745c7181e913d23de50552d0e3d38af014abe085d72f8323f8389f1642c047","item_id":"3c43257e4f:1","text":"可以从 Add（添加）菜单创建 RenderMan 灯光。"}
{"id":"ae3a1931315bbebd992d62f09b814bb6edb4c3d36eba294025dd480f29801ecc","item_id":"3c43257e4f:2","text":"Analytic Light Types（解析灯光类型）"}
{"id":"59dc61b83057c708e8cb473776e26021350e3828b3be736252555f68d1d1feda","item_id":"3c43257e4f:3","text":"有关参数的详细信息，请参阅每种灯光类型对应的链接。"}
{"id":"bce6ad691d4917ed8e21735ee38c09a3c0cb591bd13de9520c6f7f55f9d4bef9","item_id":"3c43257e4f:4","text":"PxrRectLight"}
{"id":"2cb41919bdac45bcf80dbb1cf81588845dd8d42ac05c5529b2b64673491f8f77","item_id":"3c43257e4f:5","text":"– 这是常用的矩形 area light（区域灯）"}
{"id":"b5846f52f46ec6fed4e841c80d768118053bdfbd8f85a4a8432c9414bb08ad95","item_id":"3c43257e4f:6","text":"PxrCylinderLight"}
{"id":"bd6bdf9e49afb389e57ad4ceccc66f5deb56fdad5a132f2f4dd62c3da7b5a0ff","item_id":"3c43257e4f:7","text":"– 这是常用的 cylinder area light（圆柱区域灯），用于模拟 fluorescent lights（荧光灯）和 light sabers（光剑）"}
{"id":"2098ffa4ac05d3f62dad7a01cb5066bbb463b84e5cb2cd9c4364c5bf27fafa8b","item_id":"3c43257e4f:8","text":"PxrDiskLight"}
{"id":"def6daacd11432667678e6b0b1e83b66fab76ce3109f0a92ede5681687c5f80a","item_id":"3c43257e4f:9","text":"– disk（圆盘）非常适合作为 area light（区域灯），也可与 filters（滤镜）组合来制作 spotlight（聚光灯）"}
{"id":"c0eb10eb381af128b5545089127bac4730878814b3f8f90234e161d8bb4fbc3a","item_id":"3c43257e4f:10","text":"PxrDistantLight"}
{"id":"36e7ef6b1bc1513aad4e7275be477c68265ad99ba2132dbc841de2e60b9eb597","item_id":"3c43257e4f:11","text":"– distant light（远距灯）非常适合用作 sun（太阳）或其他 distant source（远距光源）；其 light rays（光线）几乎平行，并覆盖整个场景"}
{"id":"52d7ea5640dedc6b78c114b4b9c95c38e8727f28cd01e63a0982a561cd2d54bf","item_id":"3c43257e4f:12","text":"PxrSphereLight"}
{"id":"75c4b3a2ba1ed7335b799db4e215072895c28c224be4ffc37d80b498e2a43e7b","item_id":"3c43257e4f:13","text":"– 对于仍想使用 point light（点光源）的用户，此灯光可用于向所有方向照明"}
{"id":"9023eaf38852e88f3195c6df547ee2b4e846f0045efd7c0329708a3db5975550","item_id":"3c43257e4f:14","text":"PxrAovLight"}
{"id":"bbd978246e094dda4eb2d91b48e085094dfd01dec7bb1a18b707a1f4b16900df","item_id":"3c43257e4f:15","text":"– 这是用于"}
{"id":"554f0a9ad51ef2eaeaadabe4ef71cc7a3f8ee1ed657789f7c634c4b3f73b5e4b","item_id":"3c43257e4f:16","text":"输出 AOV mask（AOV 遮罩）的 utility light（实用灯光）；由于它不照亮场景，因此没有 manipulator（操纵器）。它在场景中的位置并不重要"}
{"id":"1212e2ab64a08ec5ced8175eb4e0b702d7cfc550ede4593bd2ead1444ee69a02","item_id":"3c43257e4f:17","text":"PxrDomeLight"}
{"id":"2bd490db0749b1e3443858837420be79df3e46d041d9d6cb7d15d1f91bc9285e","item_id":"3c43257e4f:18","text":"– dome light（穹顶灯）充当场景的"}
{"id":"3d404f5d5c9d5467c91de55167985b152d14829d1b3a4783b31e446dcf84343b","item_id":"3c43257e4f:19","text":"environment light（环境光）"}
{"id":"04eb9d8f245f1a441b002b7ae4b2a1018d6ed8c2e81b6aaf9dcb924adf134fbb","item_id":"3c43257e4f:20","text":"，并使用 high dynamic range image（高动态范围图像，HDRI）进行映射，这是非常常见的工作流"}
{"id":"902e1d2a62eb9be4cffa7a5918aa7e9aecd6188f0c9abb1f12534471f681ec4c","item_id":"3c43257e4f:21","text":"PxrPortalLight"}
{"id":"072f42f1f83f2ab141dc4522bfa3116fb9579c1fd76158e5940c8fabb5e586e6","item_id":"3c43257e4f:22","text":"– 对于间接照明室内等困难 lighting situations（照明场景），此灯光可与 PxrDomeLight 搭配使用，以提升渲染质量和速度。Portal lights（门户灯）需要与 dome light（穹顶灯）关联。只需在 outliner（大纲视图）中将 portal light object（门户灯对象）作为 dome light（穹顶灯）的子级。"}
{"id":"ee57ed13ccef28fd60c0100c0f99c44fe40ca7c46ba8d37623a5ddce3072bf7b","item_id":"3c43257e4f:23","text":"PxrEnvDayLight"}
{"id":"33f59111fc6ae150fc78087746c7f25db1004c942d15c4310e4d044e1a07967d","item_id":"3c43257e4f:24","text":"– 这是一个 daylight simulation shader（日光模拟着色器）；你可以提供地球上的任意时间和位置，也可以直接把 sunlight（阳光）放在想要的位置。"}
